        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer306281695" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7449846357204965927">This really is a well researched and well written complex mystery, layers over layers. Sailor is so adept at bringing Rome alive in the time of Sulla’s waning dictatorship and just after the proscriptions. A fine balance between social and political history was achieved and it was a most enjoyable re-read.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


